<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head></head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f7; color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/miscellaneous/image/upload/v1729975173/akeurope/logo-full.png"
                style="height: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px" alt="akeurope.org Logo" />
        </div>
        <h2 style="color: #333333;">‚≠êÔ∏è Thank you for your order!</h2>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 20px 0;">

        <h3 style="color: #333333;">Payment Receipt</h3>

        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem;">
            <strong>Order No:</strong> {{ order.orderNo }}<br>
            <strong>Date:</strong> {{ order.createdAt }}<br>
            <strong>Total Amount:</strong> {{ order.total }} {{order.currency}} <br>
            <strong>Payment Method:</strong> Vipps <br>
            <strong>Status:</strong> Paid <br>
        </p>

        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 15px;">
            <thead>
                <tr style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">Product</th>
                    <th style="text-align: right; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">Cost</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each order.products}}
                {{#each this.variants}}
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; color: #333333;">{{ name }} ({{ ../name }})</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #333333;">{{quantity}} x {{ price }}
                        {{../../order.currency}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
            <tfoot>
                <tr style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
                    <td style="padding: 8px; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;">Total
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; text-align: right; font-weight: bold; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;">
                        {{ order.total }} {{order.currency}}</td>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tfoot>
        </table>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 20px 0;">

        {{#if newUser}}
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4px; margin-top: 10px;">
            We‚Äôre excited to introduce our newly built Alkhidmat Europe Customer Portal, designed to make managing your
            donations easier than ever. With this portal, you can easily track your contributions, download receipts,
            and stay informed about the impact you‚Äôre making‚Äîall in one secure place.
            <strong> Please note, the invite link below
                will expire in 24 hours.</strong>
        </p>
        <a href="{{portalUrl}}"
            style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right:20px; background-color: #007A78; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
            Invited üéä to Customer Portal
        </a>
        {{else}}
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4px; margin-top: 10px;">
            You can access your payment history, beneficiary profiles and manage your contributions anytime through the
            Alkhidmat Europe
            Customer Portal.
        </p>
        <a href="{{portalUrl}}"
            style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right:20px; background-color: #007A78; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
            Go to Customer Portal
        </a>
        {{/if}}
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem; margin-top: 10px">
            If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reply to this email or contact Abdul Wahab
            directly via WhatsApp at +47 929 21 200.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem;">
            Thank you for being part of this vital cause. Your generosity is making a real difference.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5rem;">
            With gratitude,<br>The Alkhidmat Europe Team <br> <a href="https://akeurope.org"
                style="text-decoration: none; color: #007A78">akeurope.org</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>